  "copeptin_entry_thresholds": {
    "standard_copeptin": null,
    "early_copeptin": 0.88
  },
  "clinical_interpretation": "Under standard conditions (copeptin ACS sensitivity 0.85), copeptin never enters the optimal panel\u2014it remains below \u03c4=0.90. However, in early-presenter settings (copeptin ACS sensitivity 0.90), copeptin enters the panel when hs-cTnI sensitivity drops to 0.88. This confirms the Mu et al. 2023 finding: copeptin's value is conditional on both the troponin threshold and the clinical timing. In early presentations where copeptin is at its peak sensitivity and troponin has not yet risen, copeptin provides essential ACS coverage that hs-cTnI cannot."
